(firstQuint)Surgery Treatment of Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus Patients With Grade 1 Obesity and Overweight.

 A clinical trial, 1-arm treatment (Duodenal Ileal Interposition with Sleeve Gastrectomy for Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus), including 50 research subjects with type 2 diabetes mellitus and obesity class I or overweight.

 The main objective is to analyse the effect on glycemic control after 2 years of follow-up.

